# Adapted from Example 5, Fig 5 of:
# Chen, Mingshuai et al.: "Does a Program Yield the Right Distribution? - Verifying Probabilistic Programs via Generating Functions" (CAV 2022)

X := 2;

while X != 0 unroll 1 {
    while 0 ~ Bernoulli(0.625)  {
        X += 1;
    }
    X -= 1;
    C += 1;
}
return C;

